The schedule for the 2012 National
Collegiate Athletic Association men’s basketball tournament. The
Final Four will be held March 31 and April 2 in  New Orleans . All
games televised by  CBS Sports  and Turner Broadcasting’s TBS, TNT
and truTV. All times Eastern Daylight.  To contact the reporter on this story:
